00:34:16.700 --> 00:34:18.300
live life.

00:34:18.300 --> 00:34:20.300
We have trials and circumstances.

00:34:20.300 --> 00:34:23.420
And we have things that we look at and we say,

00:34:23.420 --> 00:34:25.940
but what about this?

00:34:25.940 --> 00:34:28.740
And God says, this is no problem for me.

00:34:28.740 --> 00:34:33.380
It's just a problem for you, right?

00:34:33.380 --> 00:34:37.100
This situation was no problem for God.

00:34:37.100 --> 00:34:39.980
It was just a problem for Sarah and Abraham.

00:34:39.980 --> 00:34:42.940
And God says, isn't anything too hard for the Lord?

00:34:42.940 --> 00:34:45.580
So I don't know what your problems are this evening.

00:34:45.580 --> 00:34:49.220
And I don't use that word in a demeaning type of a way.

00:34:49.220 --> 00:34:52.420
I don't know where our doubts are this evening.

00:34:52.420 --> 00:34:56.420
But what I'd say to you is that typically, they're

00:34:56.420 --> 00:35:02.180
a result of our perspective not being where it ought to be.

00:35:02.180 --> 00:35:09.300
Because when we have a word from the Lord, do we believe him?

00:35:09.300 --> 00:35:10.780
Do we believe him?

00:35:10.780 --> 00:35:13.380
And it really just kind of boils down to that.

00:35:13.380 --> 00:35:17.620
Do we believe God?

00:35:17.620 --> 00:35:26.300
Do we judge him faithful, worthy of our trust, who has promised?

00:35:26.300 --> 00:35:30.060
Listen, get in the Bible and get some promises.

00:35:30.060 --> 00:35:32.340
I mean, study the scriptures and grab hold

00:35:32.340 --> 00:35:38.860
onto some principles and some promises and just claim them.

00:35:38.860 --> 00:35:41.700
Because God will not fail you.

00:35:41.700 --> 00:35:48.940
And Sarah, Abraham, they got to see God do something miraculous.

00:35:48.940 --> 00:35:53.700
And here we are thousands of years later reading about it.

00:35:53.700 --> 00:35:58.580
Again, familiar to most of us about Abraham and Sarah.

00:35:58.580 --> 00:36:03.620
But when we look at that pivotal moment in the life of Sarah,

00:36:03.620 --> 00:36:07.940
when did her doubt become faith?

00:36:07.940 --> 00:36:10.060
And for you this evening and for me this evening,

00:36:10.060 --> 00:36:15.060
when does our doubt become faith?

00:36:15.060 --> 00:36:17.260
We got to get into the book.

00:36:17.260 --> 00:36:19.420
We got to hear the voice of God.

00:36:19.420 --> 00:36:21.620
I'm not talking about an audible voice.

00:36:21.620 --> 00:36:24.340
I'm talking about through the pages of scripture.

00:36:24.340 --> 00:36:26.020
We hear the voice of God.

00:36:26.020 --> 00:36:27.620
So you know what?

00:36:27.620 --> 00:36:29.020
I'm going to believe God.

00:36:29.020 --> 00:36:30.060
I'm going to believe God.

00:36:30.060 --> 00:36:30.540
Let's pray.

00:36:30.540 --> 00:36:33.540
Father, we love you.

00:36:33.540 --> 00:36:34.900
We thank you for loving us.

00:36:34.900 --> 00:36:41.260
We thank you for the example this evening of Sarah.

00:36:41.260 --> 00:36:45.140
I thank you for that final statement.

00:36:45.140 --> 00:36:49.220
She judged you faithful, worthy of trust.

00:36:49.220 --> 00:36:52.540
She heard you speak those words that are recorded for us

00:36:52.540 --> 00:36:56.940
in Genesis 18 and verse 14.

00:36:56.940 --> 00:37:00.140
Is anything too hard for the Lord?

00:37:00.140 --> 00:37:04.740
At the time appointed I will and Sarah shall have a son.

00:37:04.740 --> 00:37:10.300
Oh God, thank you for ministering to Sarah,

00:37:10.300 --> 00:37:12.260
for allowing her to hear those words

00:37:12.260 --> 00:37:18.300
and for her to believe you, to trust you, to exercise faith.

00:37:21.340 --> 00:37:24.380
God, I think about my life and our lives this evening

00:37:24.380 --> 00:37:28.820
and I pray that you'd help us to be people of faith.

00:37:28.820 --> 00:37:32.980
Help us to live by faith, Lord, to believe you,

00:37:32.980 --> 00:37:37.460
to get into your word and allow your word to get into us.

00:37:37.460 --> 00:37:41.660
God, that we'd know the promises and claim the promises,

00:37:41.660 --> 00:37:45.020
that we'd see you work as only you can.

00:37:45.020 --> 00:37:47.020
Thank you for loving us.

00:37:47.020 --> 00:37:48.780
I pray that you'd bless the time of prayer

00:37:48.780 --> 00:37:51.660
that through all that's said and done you'd be glorified.

00:37:51.660 --> 00:37:53.740
For it's in Christ's name we pray.

00:37:53.740 --> 00:37:55.300
Amen.

